Sulit kupercaya.

30
00:01:30,389 --> 00:01:32,999
Kenapa kamu bilang begitu, Mi Yeon?

31
00:01:37,770 --> 00:01:39,070
Apa dia

32
00:01:40,839 --> 00:01:43,809
